Documentation

The documentation consists of manual pages as well as a manual. All documentation
is written in XML using the Docbook5 schema. All documentation except for the 
standard man pages are installed in “<PREFIX>/share/packages/g7ctrl/“. If the build is
configured as standard PREFIX is normally /usr

dbdoc - DB Schema and RNMG grammar for XML export

manpages - Unix man (1) pages for “g7ctrl” and “g7sh”

manual - A more detailed description of the daemon. The manual is available in both
HTML, PDF and text versions.



